name: Baby Bird - Jetpack Adventure
description: Fly through the air with Jetpacks and the Help of Papa Bird to escape the grasp of an evil hawk. Baby Bird Jetpack Adventure is the story of a Baby Blue Jay spreading his wings and flying for the first time to freedom. You will love this Awesome game for all ages. At first sight you will see the beautiful graphics and fun challenges in this one of a kind game. Try it out now and see how fun it really is!
